		<title>How to play bass *FAST*&#8230; 5 ultimate tips&#8230;</title>
		<link>http://www.scottsbasslessons.com/notes/play-bass-fast-5-ultimate-tips.html</link>
		<comments>http://www.scottsbasslessons.com/notes/play-bass-fast-5-ultimate-tips.html#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Mon, 27 Feb 2017 13:39:15 +0000</pubDate>
