		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.scottsbasslessons.com/?p=13659</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[<p>=== In this lesson I’m going to show you one of the most common bad habits I see beginner and intermediate bass players suffering from... I call it "the see-saw". If you do suffer from this common bad habit, playing...</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.scottsbasslessons.com/technique/bad-bass-technique-the-dreaded-see-saw.html">Bad Bass Technique: The Dreaded &#8220;See-Saw&#8221;! (L#190)</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.scottsbasslessons.com">Online Bass Lessons</a>.</p>
