		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.scottsbasslessons.com/?p=13534</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[<p>=== In this lesson you’re going to be learning all about the “One Finger Per Fret System” - and when you shouldn’t be using it. Misuse of this technique is one of the most common bad habits I see when...</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.scottsbasslessons.com/technique/one-finger-per-fret-system.html">The One Finger Per Fret System &#038; When You SHOULDN&#8217;T Use It! (L#189)</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.scottsbasslessons.com">Online Bass Lessons</a>.</p>
